<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Dinkelsbühl</head><p>Der Rat teilt die Bereitschaft des Martin N., Vikar in Nürnberg, zum Austrag am Freitag vor Michaelstag und die Rücknahme seiner Klage vor dem Landgericht mit.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_172" id="85r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_172_r1l21">Den von <expan>dınkel<ex>ſbühl</ex></expan> / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_172_r1l22"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns von <expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Merteıns <expan>vıcary<ex>er</ex></expan> bey vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_172_r1l23"><expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> habt / etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_172_r1l24">Vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mıt <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Mertein darauf geredt ſouıl . daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_172_r1l25">er vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> hat / daʒ er 
<del rend="strikethrough">des </del> auf den freıtag vor ſand </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_172_r1l26">Mıchelſtag ſchıerıſt / gen eẅch vnd den <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> des tags vor </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_173" id="85v"/><ab facs="#facs_173_r2l2">vns warten wıl ın der maſſ als Jr vns das 
<add><ab facs="#facs_173_r2l1">auf <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> nehſte ſchrıft </ab></add> <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> habt </ab> <add><ab facs="#facs_173_r1l1">da wıſſ ſıch eẅr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_173_r1l2"><expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>nachcʒurıchte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> <ab facs="#facs_173_r2l3">vnd alſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> rat mıt <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_173_r2l4"><expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Merteın geſandt / daʒ er ſein klag <expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>lantger<ex>icht</ex></expan> yecʒ gancʒ </ab><ab facs="#facs_173_r2l5">abgetan hat / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab><ab facs="#facs_173_r2l6"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> / <expan>vıgı<ex>lia</ex></expan> Matheȷ <expan>app<ex>oſto</ex>lȷ</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_172" id="85r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von <expan>Dinkel<ex>sbühl</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns von
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Merteins <expan>vicary<ex>er</ex></expan> bey
                        uns <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> habt etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Mertein darauf geredt sovil, daz er uns
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> hat, daz er <app>
<note><q type="date">auf den freitag vor sand Michelstag
                                schierist</q>27.09.1420</note>
</app> gen ewch und den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> des tags vor <pb facs="#facs_173" id="85v"/>uns warten wil, in der mass als ir uns das <add>auf
                                    <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> nehste schrift</add>
<expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> habt,
                            <add>da wiss sich ewr <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>nach czu richte<ex>n</ex></expan></add>. Und also
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> rat mit
                                <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Mertein gesandt, daz er sein klag
                                <expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>lantger<ex>icht</ex></expan> yecz gancz abgetan hat. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>vigi<ex>lia</ex></expan> Mathei
                        <expan>app<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>.</ab>
</div>
